":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ka\u2019b ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the souls of martyrs are in green birds, hanging from the fruits of Paradise, or the trees of Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1641 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0643\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15067,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/15\/allah-loves-hurrying-break-fast\/","url_meta":{"origin":13881,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Iftar: Allah loves hastening to break fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 15, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty said: The most beloved among My servants are those who are quickest to break their fast.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 700 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"al